    "attributes": {
        "action": "Reduce the number of days in a year a workers union can strike to 12 days a year",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "Over the last 12 months union strikes have disrupted public transport. At the moment operators like Northern have been striking every Saturday since October 2018. I would like to  introduce a cap of 12 days a year for unions to use for there strike days.",
